+
+  * New upstream release.
+
+ -- Shizuo Fujita <fujita@clear-code.com>  Sun, 29 Aug 2027 13:55:06 -0000
+
 fluent-package (6.0.0-1) unstable; urgency=low
 
   * New upstream release.
